{% extends 'email/base.text.twig' %}

{% block body %}
Hello,

a new support ticket has just been submitted by a customer and is waiting to be handled.

TICKET DETAILS
--------------
Ticket No.:  #{{ ticket_id }}
Subject:     {{ ticket_subject }}
Category:    {{ ticket_category }}
Priority:    {{ ticket_priority }}
Created at:  {{ ticket_created_at }}

CUSTOMER
--------
Name:  {{ customer_name }}
Email: {{ customer_email }}

CUSTOMER'S MESSAGE
------------------
{{ ticket_message }}

Open ticket in admin panel: {{ ticket_url }}
{% endblock %}
